{"tid":180702,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"當你仲飲緊津路烏龍茶既時候⋯","createTime":"2017-03-31T05:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T05:48:33.000Z","uid":3066,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40155cdfdcc8f7b9905287efdc9e7d5600cdbe2f","tid":180702,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"當你飲緊津路烏龍茶既時候<br />\n有冇發覺旁人對你既目光有所唔同？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">「果支野好好飲架！」<br />\n「條友識飲！」</span><br />\n<br />\n不過 呢家已經唔同<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">「呢家冇呢支歌仔唱架啦！」</span><br />\n<br />\n點解？不如等我話你知！<br />\n<br />\n當年既我 一日買一箱津路烏龍茶放屋企<br />\n隨時隨地飲津路烏龍茶<br />\n食飯果陣飲津路烏龍茶<br />\n沖涼又係用津路烏龍茶<br />\n俾我既感覺好似跳左落四川九寨溝到沖涼咁<br />\n<br />\n連去人地婚宴飲果陣 我都隨身帶住一支津路烏龍路<br />\n「飲杯！」「飲杯！」<br />\n「呵！個傻仔係到飲茶」<br />\n每次我俾人笑<br />\n我都同自己講 係佢地唔識欣賞only<br />\n<br />\n直至有一日<br />\n我飲左一支道地解茶<br />\n屌 真係好撚好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係動物園同緊d猩猩 馬嬲跳緊老舞咁<br />\n好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n華仔 多謝你"},{"pid":"44d5dd9df8ad4b4c5565ee74b402042e229f7098","tid":180702,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639739621b9c9b1f16c75937d3876397c6550b5a","tid":180702,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"十八茶同解茶都好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cc8434796fcc7db094d5b04f864681bb47ec06","tid":180702,"uid":74479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"你試埋用解茶沖涼先"}]}